### Atomic Design System

**61+ Components organized by complexity:**

- **Atoms** (37): Basic building blocks
  - Button, Input, Badge, Avatar, Label, Card, etc.
  - Pure presentation, CVA variants
  - Mobile-first sizing (44px+ touch targets)

- **Molecules** (12): Combinations of atoms
  - FormField, SearchBar, PhotoCarousel, etc.
  - Simple state management
  - Loading and error states

- **Organisms** (11): Complex systems
  - Navigation, ProfileCards, ToolBuilder, etc.
  - Complex interactions
  - Behavioral psychology patterns
  - Framer Motion animations

- **Templates** (1): Page layouts
  - ProfileViewLayout, DashboardLayout
